and um yeah it helps us or also kids to make more structured decisions um yeah i think that's a

00:08:47.980 --> 00:08:52.380
a very valuable skill to learn, not only for coding, but for everyday life, I guess.

00:08:52.840 --> 00:08:53.280
Yeah.

00:08:53.860 --> 00:08:55.480
Being able to break problems down and solve them.

