00:09:27.930 --> 00:09:33.060
even or especially when they fail, that they understand that failure isn't something bad,

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:36.260
but rather it keeps you improving, it keeps you going,

00:09:36.370 --> 00:09:44.160
and that you can learn to see challenges or problems at something positive

00:09:44.710 --> 00:09:46.260
and something you can grow with.

00:09:46.360 --> 00:09:52.600
I think that's really, really great about coding because you will have that a lot when you learn how to code.

