It might also not be explained in the best way, but they just shut down and say, OK, I'm just not going to try.

00:11:20.900 --> 00:11:39.960
And if you understand and maybe also I know that there's this huge psychological research on growth mindset that you understand that you shouldn't praise just an outcome, but rather the effort that kids try to do something.

